{"tid":1129032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"郭台銘稱「國防靠和平」遭曲解　「為什麼中國人要打中國人」","createTime":"2019-04-28T08:22:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T08:39:48.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c99d5e688ea26f3e3bcde6ba72ba7284174220f6","tid":1129032,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T08:22:18.000Z","msg":"郭台銘稱「國防靠和平」遭曲解　「為什麼中國人要打中國人」<br />\n<br />\n郭台銘今天下午到台中參加鄉鎮市長聯合促進會，會後受訪一開口就說，太太回家日子真好，大家要關心國家大事。他隨後即批評，看到昨天現任總統走上街頭抗公投，覺得腦筋錯亂，他們到底在朝還在野，看來他們習慣在野，「我們讓他繼續在野，街頭對抗公投這是很奇怪的議題。」<br />\n<br />\n另外郭台銘提到，外界曲解他「國防靠和平」的說法，他解釋並不是說完全不買武器，而是錢要花在刀口上，挑選有用的防禦性武器，未來將發展到無人作戰。他說，沒有一個家庭願把子女送上戰場，發展高科技未來AI（人工智慧）、8K（超高畫質電視規格），這都是他過去幾年在做的事情，<span style=\"color: red;\">他認為國防要靠和平，要實力，以和平為後盾「我們不挑釁，不懼怕，我不講不懼戰，為什麼中國人要打中國人？」</span><br />\n<br />\n郭認為，應該省下錢到全球發展科技，將來武器上至太空下至海底，全是無人；應該發展未來的無人，不該買防衛性設備，而是要買偵防、預防式的，以和平為基礎不挑釁的防衛，「我的意思被曲解，要買有用的，錢要花在刀口上。」<br />\n<br />\n被詢及下周有機會見韓國瑜會說什麼？郭台銘則說:「加油、加油！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/realtime/20190428/1557931/?utm_campaign=twad_social_apple.realtimenews&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2Frealtime%2F20190428%2F1557931%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_apple.realtimenews%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=chjGuQxbuHnWuKCrZ0Kyvg%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=a2f3ce13\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2Frealtime%2F20190428%2F1557931%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_apple.realtimenews%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=3334068c\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/realtime/20190428/1557931/?utm_campaign=twad_social_apple.realtimenews&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"363ba9932c3f6d5afdcdc00265e2c7231b6097bd","tid":1129032,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T08:23:15.000Z","msg":"幾千年黎都係咁打架啦"},{"pid":"a10233d892a2aad343ab8d77dc07e68e48aa5ff8","tid":1129032,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T08:23:57.000Z","msg":"打共匪"},{"pid":"a61dc1e6636086dae093f73a03271e738875d534","tid":1129032,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"363ba9932c3f6d5afdcdc00265e2c7231b6097bd","tid":1129032,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T08:23:15.000Z","msg":"幾千年黎都係咁打架啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T08:24:53.000Z","msg":"千多年來中原支那人侵佔其他種族人地方"},{"pid":"5557470dbc23ca702348da5a799fd0a116679b4d","tid":1129032,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T08:25:41.000Z","msg":"問下蔣介石?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"992980f2155ab11754fbc3f3ea04dd5050e4eea2","tid":1129032,"uid":1327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T08:28:07.000Z","msg":"咁天真 抵係國民黨得番個島仔<br />\n跳海死左佢算啦"},{"pid":"c9c8c5041bab2818757e9ba0f03d0f7a9e00b458","tid":1129032,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T08:28:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcSN0YsYjIKnYvSOikxEQ_RfHOskCJKyatP8tGgMcjdDXvbZ2m5X\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcSN0YsYjIKnYvSOikxEQ_RfHOskCJKyatP8tGgMcjdDXvbZ2m5X&h=b528f8d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d81d6108acff27cf0187184cea6aa896818138f","tid":1129032,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T08:30:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/73768_198262320319177_360074094_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.l